creator: Ezheights FZ LLC
descriptionHtml:
Over 100,000 downloads!

Biggit is your one-stop online portal for buying and selling just about every product and service you could need!
Biggit's easy-to-navigate layout makes it simple for sellers to target the right buyers – and for buyers to find exactly what they’re looking for. It’s a win-win situation for both!

Looking for a home or office? Find from a variety of apartments, hotel apartments, commercial buildings, offices, villas and all other types of properties for rent or sale. Get exactly what you're looking for with search filters - search by category, area (community), city, price, size and even tower name - yes, it's that advanced and accurate!

Want to drive home a new car or bike? Or maybe surf through the waves on a new boat or yacht? Biggit makes it possible!
Search for cars, bikes, boats, yachts, accessories, parts and even commercial vehicles. Filter your search by brand name, make, etc.

Buying or selling your old stuff, or stuff you've made, is also possible on Biggit. The classifieds section is a great place to find new buyers - be it for your old stuff or for your new creations! Make home improvement easy, right on your fingertips.
Buy and sell ANYTHING - antiques, appliances, electronics, books, audio, beauty, health, jewelry, watches, cameras, musical equipment, clothing, sporting goods, furniture, art, gaming equipment, consoles, games, toys, bicycles, gadgets and baby items too.

What's more, you can even experience the age-old trading tradition of the Barter system - exchange your stuff with equally awesome stuff from someone reliable.

Biggit can also help you advance your career or your business - find a job or your next best hire. Upload your CV/Resume or your job description and filter your search according to industry, category, location, experience and salary range. After all, the best way to predict the future is to create it.

Last but not the least, our community section helps you find and offer all kinds of services - trainers, artists, babysitters, elderly home assistants, house help, musicians, pet sitters, rideshare and carpools, home repairmen, medical services and electricians. Get anything done - or find new clients.

Why advertise with us?
Our website’s advanced algorithm and revolutionary technology ensure your listings can be found quickly and easily by potential buyers. Fully optimized for all devices, it doesn’t matter whether they are searching on a PC, Mac, tablet or mobile – they can find you.

So take Biggit wherever you are, for whatever you need. Currently available in USA, UAE, Jordan and India. We're expanding globally, fast. So let us know which country you want to use Biggit in and we'll be there soon!

Thanks to all our loyal fans for your support. Got feedback or suggestions? Please email us at naumaan@alogr8.com.

descriptionHtml:
Biggit is your one-stop trusted classifieds website and app to buy and sell anything and everything! Think of it as your very own online flea market that lets you find the best deals and offers on second hand and pre-owned items.

Home to a wide collection of new and pre-owned products from electronics,
furniture, pre-owned cars, games, jobs to property for sale and flats for Rent in Dubai, India, USA and Philippine.

Biggit is the largest classifieds app for buying and selling, whether in India, UAE, Bahrain, USA, or the Philippines. With over 100,000 downloads and 300,000 listings and counting, Biggit has grown to be the prime destination to buy and sell cars in Dubai, post free classifieds ads in Dubai, India, or the Philippines to finding jobs.

You can browse through our range of diverse categories:

Real Estate:
Looking to relocate? Hunting for an apartment, studio, 1, 2, or 3 BHK, or a villa in your favourite location? Biggit makes your search easy. With a large selection of listings directly from landlords and homeowners, you get to find your dream home on Biggit.

Motors
From popular brands of cars to luxurious vehicles, get your favourite set of wheels on Biggit. From a two-wheeler to a four-wheeler, Biggit has got it all covered for you.

Mobiles
Ring out the old, ring in the new! Mobiles are one of the most popular categories yet on Biggit, with our Biggit cave stacked with top brands. Biggit lets you buy and sell your mobile phone easily. Now, you can upgrade to the latest Android or iOS version by choosing from a wide selection of phones. Apart from mobiles, Biggit also offers headphones, chargers, power banks, and memory cards.

Classifieds
Can’t afford that beautiful dress you saw in the mall? Well, there are a lot more options for every budget at Biggit, home to a wide selection of vacation wear, formal attire, and casual wear. From dresses for women and shirts for men to footwear for men and women and lifestyle accessories. The classifieds category is filled with choices from musical instruments, furniture, antiques, and collectibles to audio and stereo.

Electronics
Biggit is your favourite tech haunt yet! Explore our wide and unstoppable range of electronics for your newly bought apartment or studio. Whether you want to buy or sell unused electronics or appliances, Biggit is your go-to trusted online platform. Covering refrigerators, laptops, computers, washing machines, household appliances, sofa sets, wardrobe, television sets, and more.

Community
From a mechanic to a plumber, find the right one instantly. Dive into a sea of
choices through our friendly and easy-to-use app. And every bit as safe! Whether you are looking for electrical services in UAE, home repair services in India, or babysitters in the USA, Biggit is the app that fixes all your worries.

Jobs
Looking for a job? It’s never too small when it’s Biggit! Find your dream job,
through a selection of job vacancies in Dubai, India, USA, or Philippine.
Browse from banking, IT jobs in Dubai, hospitality jobs in India, engineering
jobs in the USA, marketing to sales jobs, and more in the UAE, India, Bahrain,
Philippine, and USA. All you have to do is upload your resume and start applying for the job of your dream. Whether you are looking for a job in media, event management, or banking and construction, Biggit is your trusted platform to find the right one.

Highlights of Biggit App:
●Buy and sell anything and everything under one cave.
●Chat with the seller directly to get the right price for the product.
●24/7 Customer Support available.
●Recommendations and alerts based on your interests.

So, what’s holding you back? Download the Biggit classifieds app and be a part of our caveman’s club. Connect with millions of buyers and sellers instantly!
